data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET AT NO FAULT OF SELLER OR HOME!  Price Improvement!     This magnificent home is nestled on a sprawling 1.16-acre lot, offering plenty of space and privacy. As you approach the residence, you're greeted by a beautifully landscaped front yard with lush greenery and an inviting entrance. Upon entering the main floor you are greeted by the spacious layout, featuring a formal living room, a dining area, and a cozy family room with large windows that flood the space with natural light. The main floor also features a guest bedroom, full bathroom, and laundry room which host additional storage space. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight hosting a large center island with a breakfast bar, ample storage space, and exquisite countertops. Adjacent to the kitchen, there's a breakfast nook where you can enjoy your morning coffee while taking in the scenic views of the backyard. Upstairs features your owner's suite and two additional bedrooms. The owner's suite is a true sanctuary, complete with a luxurious en-suite bathroom featuring a soaking tub, a separate shower, dual vanity sinks, and a large walk-in closet. The remaining bedrooms are well-appointed, with comfortable layouts and easy access to the additional bathrooms. One of the standout features of this home is the partially finished basement which offers a bedroom, full bathroom, office suite with built-in bookcases, and an entertainment room. There is an additional versatile space that can be used as a recreational area, a home gym, or a media room tailored to your preferences. The basement also includes ample storage options to keep your belongings organized. As you step outside, you'll discover a backyard oasis designed for relaxation and entertainment. The centerpiece is a magnificent saltwater pool, perfect for cooling off during hot summer days or enjoying a refreshing swim. Surrounding the pool, there's a spacious patio area where you can set up outdoor furniture and host memorable gatherings with family and friends. The expansive yard beyond the pool offers endless possibilities for gardening, recreation, or even adding additional amenities such as a playground or a gazebo. The property also features a two-car garage, providing secure parking and additional storage space. This beautiful home is located in a well-kept community with no HOA. Contact us today to see your new home!
